<p>Security is on the brain this week! Learn how to secure your iCloud account and also learn how to secure your entire home network from your ISP&#039;s prying eyes! Dave and John also help you determine what devices and processes are using your network, and what the difference is between WPA2 Personal and Enterprise. All of this and more in this week&#039;s Mac Geek Gab. Press play and enjoy!Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
